attributes.visState: {"title":"SAS Update Checker","type":"markdown","params":{"fontSize":12,"openLinksInNewTab":true,"markdown":"The SAS Update Checker Report is derived from the SAS Update Checker cron job which builds a report comparing the currently deployed release with available releases in the upstream repository. The report is written to the stdout of the launched job pod and indicates when new content related to the deployment is available.  More information about SAS Update Checker can be found here: \n\nhttps://go.documentation.sas.com/doc/en/itopscdc/v_012/k8sag/p1it185kd37v25n1aoybu799tpk4.htm"},"aggs":[]}
